Stage 3 — Docker Compose

You created:

docker-compose.yml

Purpose:

Run multiple containers together.

Instead of running:

docker run frontend
docker run backend
docker run postgres
docker run nginx

You run one command:

docker compose up --build

Compose automatically:

builds images

creates containers

creates network

connects services

Stage 4 — Docker Networking

